Ukubulawa kwababili ngoLwesine kwenze isibalo sababulewe sanyukela kwabathathu njengoba kukhona obulawe ngeledlule. Esigamekweni sangeledlule kubikwa ukuthi kudutshulwe owesilisa oneminyaka engu-26 obesendaweni yokucima ukoma, iChiefs Tarven, eseduze kwaleli hostela. Kwenzeka lesi sigameko nje kuthiwa ezinsukwini ezintathu ngaphambi kwaso kudutshulwe itekisi lesinye isakhamuzi sakhona ebelipakile eduze kwale ndawo yokucima ukoma kodwa kwangalimala muntu. Esigamekweni sokubulawa kwababili ngoLwesine, okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uLieutenant Colonel Thulani Zwane, uthe kuvulwe amacala amabili okubulala nelokuzama ukubulala. UZwane unxuse abahlali bakuleli hostela ukuthi bangakuvumeli ukucasulwa wudlame olukule ndawo bese beziphendulela. Uthe ucela basebenzisane namaphoyisa ngoba kumanje asebenza kanzima ukuthola ababulali. Leli hostela elihlala abantu abalinganiselwa ku-22 000 lihlaselwe ukubulalana kwabantu. Kusuka ngoDisemba nyakenye kuboshwe abesilisa abayishiyagalombili kuleli hostela abasolwa ngoxhaxha lwamacala okubulala khona. - ANA